                <p><b>Sappi Europe’s Policy for handling your personal data</b></p>
<p>Sappi Europe S.A. and its affiliated group companies <b>(“Sappi” or “we”</b>) are fully committed to protecting your personal data when using or processing them and recognize the importance of correct and lawful treatment of personal data.</p>
<p>Therefore, Sappi handles your personal data with <b>utmost care</b> and in <b>strict compliance</b> with applicable data protection laws, in particular the EU General Data Protection Regulation 2016/679 of 27 April 2016<sup>1</sup> and all relevant national measures.</p>
<p><b>How Sappi implements protection of your personal data in practice</b></p>
